              "bit_width": 7,
              "description": "7-bit counter (MSB to LSB) These bits contain the value of the watchdog counter, decremented every (4096 x 2WDGTB[1:0]) PCLK cycles. A reset is produced when it is decremented from 0x40 to 0x3F (T6 becomes cleared).",
